<A NAME="links"><H2>Relevant links</H2></A>

<BLOCKQUOTE>
Links to related projects:<BR>

<UL>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.cs.uoregon.edu/research/paracomp/pdtoolkit/">The
Program Database Toolkit</A> &nbsp [required by Chasm for C/C++ language
parsing]
<LI><A HREF="http://sourceforge.net/projects/gfortran2xml/">The gfortran2xml
project</A> [required for Fortran parsing]
<LI><A HREF="http://www.cca-forum.org/">Common Component Architecture</A>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.llnl.gov/CASC/components/babel.html">Babel</A> &nbsp
[a language interoperability project based on an Interface Definition
Language (IDL)]
</UL>

</BLOCKQUOTE>


